Package: pensar
Type: Package
Title: Lightweight Knowledge Graph from Markdown Files
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Troy", "Hernandez", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "troy@cornball.ai",
    comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-4248-604X"))
Description: Maintains a lightweight knowledge graph derived from markdown
    files with 'YAML' frontmatter and typed links. Parses markdown into a TSV
    index, supports graph traversal queries, suggests typed relations from
    untyped links, and emits OBO format snapshots.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/cornball-ai/pensar
BugReports: https://github.com/cornball-ai/pensar/issues
Imports:
    yaml
Suggests:
    tinytest
Encoding: UTF-8
